    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Not always you can run tests via IDE. Sometimes configs are complected and it is much easier just to type <pre> $ mvn test </pre></p>

<p>If you want to debug them, you can connect via remote.</p>

<ol>
<li>run you test <pre>$ mvn test -Dmaven.surefire.debug </pre> maven will prepare environment and will wait for remote connection</li>

<li>connect via Idea <img src="/images/2011-01-20-how-to-debug-tests-maven-test-via-intellij-idea/01.png"></li>

<li>start debug <br /> <p>
<img src="/images/2011-01-20-how-to-debug-tests-maven-test-via-intellij-idea/02.png">
</p></li>

<li>Now test will stop at your breakpoints. Profit!</li>
</ol>]]></content>
